Dictionary of Filters

Source: R/mlr_filters.R

A simple Dictionary storing objects of class Filter. Each Filter has an associated help page, see mlr_filters_[id].

Format

R6Class object

Usage

See Dictionary.

See also

Other Filter: Filter, mlr_filters_auc, mlr_filters_cmim, mlr_filters_disr, mlr_filters_gain_ratio, mlr_filters_information_gain, mlr_filters_jmim, mlr_filters_jmi, mlr_filters_kruskal_test, mlr_filters_linear_correlation, mlr_filters_mim, mlr_filters_njmim, mlr_filters_rank_correlation, mlr_filters_symmetrical_uncertainty, mlr_filters_variance

Examples

mlr_filters$keys()
#>  [1] "auc"                     "cmim"                   
#>  [3] "disr"                    "gain_ratio"

#>  [9] "linear_correlation"      "mim"                    
#> [11] "njmim"                   "rank_correlation"       
#> [13] "symmetrical_uncertainty" "variance"

#>   Inherits from: <Filter>

#>     .calculate: function (task)
